headline: Does the Cummins Rally Still Have Room After Strong 2024 Performance?
summary: If you are standing on the sidelines wondering what to do with Cummins stock, you are not alone. With a strong climb of 29.6% over the past year and triple-digit returns over the last three years, the stock seems to have attracted both seasoned investors and newcomers alike. After all, it is not every day you see a stock up 106.5% over three years, especially in an industry often regarded as mature. But before you make your next move, let's talk about what is really happening under the hood...
